{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"56c4bbff98","title":"争取东北军工作是党争取全国友军工作的重要环节","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a2aacd4c25","index":0,"year":1940,"month":6,"day":13,"articleId":"56c4bbff98"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji15.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji15":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"67b3e33ad5","type":"paragraph","text":"争取东北军工作是党争取全国友军工作的重要环节","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"56c4bbff98"},{"id":"dd62615a73","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年6月13日）东北军在抗日战争中是一支较可靠的友军，在国共斗争中基本上是一种中间势力，且有可能为我争取。我们对东北军的关系好坏，对于我们争取广大友军工作有较大的影响。因此，必须把争取东北军工作看成党争取全国友军工作的重要环节[1]这是毛泽东和王样等关于争职东北军工作致中原局，刘少奇、陈","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"56c4bbff98"}],"page":{"id":"6b0bdd2d60","publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"56c4bbff98","start":68,"end":68}}}},"__N_SSG":true}